org.midao.jdbc.core.processor

Class ExtendedQueryInputProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.midao.jdbc.core.processor.BasicQueryInputProcessor
      • org.midao.jdbc.core.processor.ExtendedQueryInputProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryInputProcessor

    public class ExtendedQueryInputProcessor
extends BasicQueryInputProcessor
    Extension of basic QueryInputProcessor implementation: BasicQueryInputProcessor.

    Only difference from parent BasicQueryInputProcessor - is that is processes "#{xxx}" instead of ":xxx". That change would allow to process parameters which can include not only parameter name, but type like: "#{xxx,jdbcType=VARCHAR}"

    Please be careful as currently only "jdbcType" (varchar/int; types which listed in MjdbcTypes) and "mode" (in, out, inout; as listed in QueryParameters.Direction) are supported.
